b'[<p><i><b>UFC 55: Fury</b></i> was a <a href="/wiki/Mixed_martial_arts" title="Mixed martial arts">mixed martial arts</a> event held by the <a href="/wiki/Ultimate_Fighting_Championship" title="Ultimate Fighting Championship">Ultimate Fighting Championship</a> on October 7, 2005 at the <a href="/wiki/Mohegan_Sun_Arena" title="Mohegan Sun Arena">Mohegan Sun Arena</a> in <a href="/wiki/Uncasville,_Connecticut" title="Uncasville, Connecticut">Uncasville, Connecticut</a>. The event was broadcast live on <a href="/wiki/Pay-per-view" title="Pay-per-view">pay-per-view</a> in the <a href="/wiki/United_States" title="United States">United States</a>, and later released on <a href="/wiki/DVD" title="DVD">DVD</a>. This would be the last UFC to air live on a Friday until <a href="/wiki/UFC_141" title="UFC 141">UFC 141</a>, which aired on December 30, 2011.\n</p>]'